Frank Evans (general) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frank_Evans_(general) 0 Frank Edgar Evans (19 November 1876 – 25 November 1941) served as an infantryman in the Spanish–American War, and was commissioned in the United States Marine Corps on 15 February 1900.
